<rte>
  <name>Moonshiner28</name>
  <desc>Moonshiner 28, beginning at the Tail of the Dragon on US 129, extends 103 miles southeast through western North Carolina (Franklin and Highlands) before continuing into Georgia and South Carolina, ultimately reaching Walhalla. Once one of the major runs for moonshiners, the road today boasts great twisties, wide sweepers and unmatched scenery.</desc>
  <extensions>
    <line xmlns="http://www.topografix.com/GPX/gpx_style/0/2">
    <color>2D3FC7</color>
    </line>
  </extensions>
